Status report of Yi Tong Tse on 9/25/98
---------------------------------------

Commented on the DPI patent draft from the patent attorney.
Written up a description for time stamp correction in the patent.

Finished writing and debugging the MPEG-2 encoder.  The encoder can now
generate I/P/B pictures.

Fixed some more bugs in the MPEG-2 decoder.  The decoder can now decode
all EchoStar bitstreams as well as HITS bitstreams.

